snippet: Kentavious Caldwell-Pope scored 13 of his 26 points in Detroit's dominating third quarter, and the Pistons set a season high for points while rolling to a 136-106 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Saturday night....

headline.main: Fitzgerald Scores Tournament-Record 30 as Temple Advances
headline.print_headline: Fitzgerald Scores Tournament-Record 30 as Temple Advances

lead_paragraph: Kentavious Caldwell-Pope scored 13 of his 26 points in Detroit's dominating third quarter, and the Pistons set a season high for points while rolling to a 136-106 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Saturday night.
